$ ORA-65318: query to cross-container fixed tables not allowed

The following query throws *ORA-65318: query to cross-container fixed tables not allowed*:
code {
select * from → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/instance/fixed-tables/comvw;
code }

sa:
  → development/databases/Oracle/architecture/instance/fixed-tables[Fixed tables]

  → development/databases/Oracle/errors[Other Oracle error messages]
